{"word":"G893 - ἀψευδής - apseudḗs - aps-yoo-dace' - That cannot lie","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀψευδής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apseudḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">aps-yoo-dace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">That cannot lie</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பொய்யுரையாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without lie, truthful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5579 - ψεῦδος - pseûdos - psyoo'-dos/5579\">G5579</a>; <i>veracious:</i> - that cannot lie.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5571/5571\">G5571</a>, <a href=\"#/G5572/5572\">G5572</a>, <a href=\"#/G5573/5573\">G5573</a>, <a href=\"#/G5574/5574\">G5574</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575/5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576/5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577/5577\">G5577</a>, <a href=\"#/G5578/5578\">G5578</a>, <a href=\"#/G5579/5579\">G5579</a>, <a href=\"#/G5580/5580\">G5580</a>, <a href=\"#/G5581/5581\">G5581</a>, <a href=\"#/G5582/5582\">G5582</a>, <a href=\"#/G5583/5583\">G5583</a>, <a href=\"#/G893/893\">G893</a>"}]}